request.doc:
POST https://{appliance_hostname}/isam/net/lookup

POST_DATA:
{
    "host":"ibm.com"
}

To specify a particular DNS:
POST_DATA:
{
    "host":"ibm.com",
    "server":"9.9.9.9"
}

response.doc:
200 OK Content-Type:application/json { "output":"Server: 192.168.42.2nAddress 1: 192.168.42.2nnName: ibm.comnAddress 1: 129.42.38.10nAddress 2: 129.42.38.10", "rc":0 }
Note that the output contains newline characters 'n'. The above response, formatted:
{ "output": "Server: 192.168.42.2 Address 1: 192.168.42.2
Name: ibm.com Address 1: 129.42.38.10 Address 2: 129.42.38.10", "rc":0 }
